{"tid":1055530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊朗男子當眾向女友求婚雙雙被捕 警方：受腐敗西方文化影響","createTime":"2019-03-10T15:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T23:17:42.000Z","uid":28765,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcd2a95862c853ef63e3949d209086155230815","tid":1055530,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T15:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190310/s00005/04e12932a691cdc7dca807d9d7b393ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190310%2Fs00005%2F04e12932a691cdc7dca807d9d7b393ec.jpg&h=c9ca17d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（Twitter影片截圖）<br />\n <br />\n伊朗北部城市阿拉克（Arak）一名男子日前在商場內，當眾向女友求婚，影片在網上流傳，事後警方以違反伊斯蘭教教義為由拘捕二人，稱他們受「腐敗的西方文化影響」，現時他們獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳影片所見，一名男子在以玫瑰花瓣砌成的心形中向女友求婚，不少途人停下圍觀及拍攝，女方答應求婚後，二人擁抱，現場傳出歡呼聲。<br />\n<br />\n事後警方以違反伊斯蘭教教義為由拘捕二人，稱他們「侮辱公眾道德，這是腐敗的西方文化影響」。警方副指揮官卡拉吉（Mahmoud Khalaji）表示，拘捕行動為「公眾要求」，現時他們已獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n（英國廣播公司）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20190310/s00005/1552207159441/%E3%80%90%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E3%80%91%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%95%B6%E7%9C%BE%E5%90%91%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E6%B1%82%E5%A9%9A%E9%9B%99%E9%9B%99%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%8F%97%E8%85%90%E6%95%97%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20190310%2Fs00005%2F1552207159441%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%259C%2597%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A9%259A%25E9%259B%2599%25E9%259B%2599%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%2585%2590%25E6%2595%2597%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF&d=NaAPOzxPFgptGlwmN